{"tid":1490351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果：斬人案女傷者係信報記者","createTime":"2019-08-20T05:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:00:40.000Z","uid":22556,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bf638fcb62c6acc9bb7f837308a2ac1d18d6da8c","tid":1490351,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"將軍澳連儂隧道斬人案，3名傷者中，送伊利沙伯醫院的26歲姓黃女傷者，目前情況危殆，數名朋友在病房外守候，憂心忡忡至於另一名受襲的24歲男子，已經出院；另一名 35 歲受傷女子，現時仍然在將軍澳醫院留醫。消息稱，重傷的是信報副刊記者黃靜美智子，她傷勢雖然嚴重但仍清醒。據悉，傷者美智子在信報副刊版主要負責家居及飲食範疇的人物專訪，朋友容形她文靜，愛寫作，並支持反送中抗爭運動。但早前多名反送中抗爭者自殺，令她情緒因而低落。 <br />\n<br />\n有傳媒引述《信報》發言人指，《信報》讉責兇徒的為暴行，並對同事受傷表示非常痛心。"},{"pid":"0cd4a6126f0383f66868e343dd78e9f48b9daa1e","tid":1490351,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4dc615c8fbdc64b405a3019f6e0f54ebc875f7","tid":1490351,"uid":99856,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"黃靜美智子 日本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bfcde3f8865a78f0f783327d5f2a5267a6b2f7","tid":1490351,"uid":39251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"反了 反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce28d583d9c8e31eb401be1bc95f02901382eb0","tid":1490351,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"美智子加油"},{"pid":"82a982e3224612d1ddc0c7a7d6cb8dffc80abb8f","tid":1490351,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"《信報財經新聞》（簡稱《信報》，英文：Hong Kong Economic Journal）係香港一份中文報紙，1973年7月創刊，主要報導財經新聞，亦有講文化嘅副